Preview Forge introduces the "3-DD Methodology" (PreviewDD · SpecDD · TestDD)
and is a self-contained Claude Code plugin distributed via GitHub-hosted
marketplace. The plugin bundles its own 143-agent engineering organization,
hook-based policy enforcement, memory system (LESSONS/PROGRESS/CLAUDE.md),
and design studio fallback. It has no third-party service dependencies.

Built with:
  - Claude Opus 4.7 (Anthropic)
  - Claude Code (Anthropic)
  - Claude Managed Agents (Anthropic, beta)
  - Anthropic Memory Tool (memory_20250818)
  - Context Editing (context-management-2025-06-27)
  - Compaction (compact_20260112)
  - Task Budgets (task-budgets-2026-03-13)
  - NestJS + @nestia/core + @nestia/sdk + typia (MIT)
  - Next.js + React (MIT)
  - Prisma (Apache-2.0)
